The paper discusses the impact of personalized AI explanations on compliance behavior, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of machine learning algorithms and their impact on compliance behavior falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the potential risks and challenges related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and compliance (cs.CR). Finally, the paper emphasizes the importance of personalization, which is a key aspect of machine learning (cs.LG).
